TROUBLESHOOTING
---------------
  "Is there a repository at the following location?"
    → The repository has not been initialised or the repo path is wrong.
      Verify RESTIC_REPOSITORY and that the Storage Box is reachable via SSH.

  "Fatal: wrong password or no key"
    → The RESTIC_PASSWORD value is incorrect.
      Re-retrieve from 1Password (item: {{ synology_restic_backup_op_restic_repo_item }}).

  "Permission denied (publickey)"
    → The SSH key in ~/.ssh/storagebox-key does not match the key authorised
      on the Storage Box. Re-retrieve from 1Password:
      {{ synology_restic_backup_op_storagebox_ssh_key_item }}

  restic check errors (pack files missing/corrupted):
    → Run: restic rebuild-index
      Then retry: restic check
      If data loss is indicated, restore from the most recent clean snapshot.
